title: Kiss Man Man Medium Light Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic kiss between two men, with specific skin tone variations. It conveys love, affection, and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts two men sharing a tender kiss, rendered with Apple’s signature smooth gradients and subtle 3D shading. The individuals, presented with medium-light and medium-dark skin tones, are drawn with soft, rounded edges and a gentle, romantic expression, embodying affection and intimacy. The realistic lighting on Apple devices highlights the closeness of the couple, making it a powerful symbol of love and partnership in digital communication.
